		<div class="post">
			<h1>Almost there!</h1>
			<p class="meta"><a href="http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/category/news" title="View all posts in News" rel="category tag">News</a> &middot; June 23rd, 2010 &middot;  <a href="http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/author/osp/" title="Posts by OSP">OSP</a></p>
			<div class="entry">
				<p><a href='http://www.pledgie.com/campaigns/8926'><img alt='Click here to lend your support to: Libre Graphics Meeting 2010 and make a donation at www.pledgie.com !' src='http://stdin.fr/lgm/pledgie/pledgie_banner.png' border='0' /></a></p>
<p>We&#8217;re busy closing the books on LGM 2010 and soon deciding where to go for LGM 2011 (Brasil? Montreal? Vietnam? Follow the discussion at: <a href="http://lists.freedesktop.org/mailman/listinfo/create">http://lists.freedesktop.org/mailman/listinfo/create</a>) so we almost did not notice that it&#8217;s only a <em>very</em> little stretch to our initial goal of raising 10.000$ on Pledgie <img src='http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':-)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
							</div>
			<p class="meta">Tags:  &middot; <a href="http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/tag/lgm-2010" rel="tag">LGM 2010</a></p>
		</div>
			<div class="clear"></div>
		
				</div><!--wide_post-->
</div><!--left_side-->

