			<div class="entry">
				<p>not for living 1/3 of my life in Brazil, but i think would be awesome having LGM there &#8211; i don&#8217;t know how far people envolved with software libre in graphic design would interest on host this kind of meeting with this importance, and even which city were mostly suitable for hosting it (Porto Alegre (hosts FISL meetings), Curitiba, São Paulo, Goiânia (interesting case study of brazilian graphic design, maybe they use software libre a lot as well?), Belo Horizonte, Recife, etc.) &#8211; would be interesting seeing comments from actually brazilian-living people below! <img src='http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
 
